{"tid":1198234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【佔中案判刑】陳淑莊判入獄8個月 緩刑兩年","createTime":"2019-06-10T07:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T10:48:09.000Z","uid":235152,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4482d793decc8eda2a0b32958f151f88e45c061b","tid":1198234,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:28:28.000Z","msg":"佔領三子及另外六名參與者被裁定串謀作出公眾妨擾等罪罪成，4月底其中八人已分別被判監或緩刑等。而面對兩項罪名的立法會議員陳淑莊，則因發現腦內有腫瘤，需緊急動手術，判刑押後至今天。辯方今早向法庭呈交陳淑莊的最新醫療報告，透露其腦部腫瘤屬良性，但因部份腫瘤壓住腦幹而未能完全移除，需在3個月內接受30期的放射性治療。辯方續指，若不進行有關治療，餘下的腫瘤部份不但未能移除，還會繼續增大。辯方又透露，陳於手術後出現後遺症，現時日常生活包括步行，均需要他人協助。法官終判陳入獄8個月緩刑兩年，散庭後庭內外掌聲不絕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190610/59696936\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190610%2F59696936&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCC%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=65fd4d8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190610%2F59696936&h=4ef6bcdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190610/59696936</a>"},{"pid":"7912419bfeaa486e88338a62b160e211f632d319","tid":1198234,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:29:40.000Z","msg":"唔駛DQ?"},{"pid":"39e9068a8ae86854a10a88f14c44d6d72df75d0f","tid":1198234,"uid":42804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7912419bfeaa486e88338a62b160e211f632d319","tid":1198234,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:29:40.000Z","msg":"唔駛DQ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:30:24.000Z","msg":"下屆冇得選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7c9c7f6e48a3a2ad59e1cc7f9095f75c40ea33","tid":1198234,"uid":34409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"39e9068a8ae86854a10a88f14c44d6d72df75d0f","tid":1198234,"uid":42804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7912419bfeaa4